<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Everyone here is right.  Use Pacification.  Placate doesn't prevent 'direct' aggro, only 'assist' aggro.   You can't 'sneak past' mobs using it (which, incidentally, is why this change was made.  Sony got tired of people using Pacification to skip content.)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
