<span class="postbody">I stand on the center platform and cast pacification as soon as they are in range and then start a mental countdown in my head.   Thirty seconds is a safe estimate for pacification timer.  
<br />

<br />
You will also use placate on this trial.  Right before you loot the last coin to get you to 300 have everyone run to the back of the room and put their asses to the wall.   Cast placate on both of the guards and have the tank pull the boss.  He should come single.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
